---

<BaseLayout
  title="Wire Mesh Belt Conveyors: Weave Types, Temperature Ranges & Applications"
  description="Wire mesh belt conveyors handle extreme temperatures from -60F to 2,100F. Balanced weave, compound balanced, and chain-edge designs for ovens, freezers, and washdown zones."
  canonical="https://packagingconveyor.com/conveyor-types/wire-mesh-conveyors/"
